"'''Camie's Story'''" is a short story written by [[Grant S. Boucher]], originally published in ''[[Galaxy Guide 1: A New Hope]]'' and ''[[The Movie Trilogy Sourcebook]]''. It was later archived on [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]].

{{Shortstory-stub}}

==Plot summary==
[[Camie Loneozner]]'s recollections of [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and his relationship with [[Owen Lars/Legends|Owen]] and [[Beru Whitesun Lars/Legends|Beru Lars]], as told to [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] [[Historian/Legends|historian]] [[Voren Na'al/Legends|Voren Na'al]].

